This file marks the repository as the AI Tech Lead Framework template itself.

The docs-sync-check CI workflow uses this marker to skip framework-state checks
that would (correctly) fail against the unbootstrapped template — checks like
"CLAUDE.md does not contain DEFAULTS BELOW" or "copilot-instructions.md exists"
are meant for consumer repos that have already run /bootstrap.

DO NOT copy this file when adopting the framework into your project. It must
exist only in the source-of-truth template repository.
